OL,3,CRed extreme heat warning announced for
OL,4,Cparts of Wales
OL,6,FThe Met Office has announced a rare
OL,7,Fred weather warning for extreme heat
OL,8,Fcovering south east Wales and central
OL,9,Fand southern England on Wednesday and
OL,10,FThursday.
OL,12,FThe red warning takes effect from 9am
OL,13,Fon Wednesday, lasting until 9pm on
OL,14,FThursday,.
OL,16,FThis week is already expected to break
OL,17,Frecords for the hottest June
OL,18,Ftemperatures, with an amber warning
OL,19,Fand health alerts in place.
OL,21,FWhat does a red warning mean?
